channel.title: Just cant understand why? HELP!
channel.description:
hi,
i was adding GlobalObjects to my server and it comes up with: [code] client.java:28765: cannot find symbol symbol : method makeGlobalObjects(int,int,int,int,int) location: class client makeGlobalObjects(3226, 3209, 6909, 0, 10); // Wall ^ Note: stream.java uses or overrides a deprecated API. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:deprecation for details. 1 error Press any key to continue . . . [/code]
But I dont understand, Code I added: [code] public void NewObjects() { makeGlobalObjects(3226, 3209, 6909, 0, 10); // Wall } [/code]
Im not sure what the problem is, Could Someone Help,
Thanks In Advance,
Jamie.
